high_descs: Turn around to face the towel hanging to the right of the mirror.
Take the towel down from the towel ring on the wall.
Turn around and stand in front of the toilet.
Put the towel on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a towel on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: turn around go to the towel hook that is hanging on the right side of the mirror
take the towel from the hook
turn around and carry the towel to the toilet
place the towel on the tank of the toilet on the right side
anns.task_desc: Put a towel on top of the toilet tank

high_descs: Turn around and look up at the small towel rack to the right of the sink
Remove the hand towel from the rack
Turn around and walk over to the toilet
Put the hand towel on the toilet right of the spray bottle
anns.task_desc: Put the hand towel on the toilet
